'''伽利略'''，多数情况下简称'''伽'''、'''Gal'''，是一个[[加速度|加速度]]单位，常用于[[重力场|重力场]]的测定。<ref>Barry N. Taylor, ''Guide for the Use of the International System of Units (SI),'' 1995, [[NIST|NIST]] Special Publication 811, [http://physics.nist.gov/Pubs/SP811/appenB9.html#ACCELERATION Appendix B] {{Wayback|url=http://physics.nist.gov/Pubs/SP811/appenB9.html#ACCELERATION |date=20160127082812 }}.</ref><ref name="SIbrochure">[[國際度量衡局|BIPM]] ''SI brochure'', 8th ed. 2006, [http://www.bipm.org/en/si/si_brochure/chapter4/table9.html Table 9: Non-SI units associated with the CGS and the CGS-Gaussian system of units] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bipm.org/en/si/si_brochure/chapter4/table9.html |date=20071018031134 }}.</ref><ref>Some sources, such as the [http://www.unc.edu/~rowlett/units/dictG.html University of North Carolina] {{Wayback|url=http://www.unc.edu/~rowlett/units/dictG.html |date=20120218191001 }}, the [http://www.esa.int/esaLP/ESAK4XZK0TC_LPgoce_0.html European Space Agency] {{Wayback|url=http://www.esa.int/esaLP/ESAK4XZK0TC_LPgoce_0.html |date=20090302163947 }}, and [http://www.conversiontables.info/index.php5?page=conversion_factors&item=Acceleration%20%5Bgeneric%5D ConversionTables.com] {{Wayback|url=http://www.conversiontables.info/index.php5?page=conversion_factors&item=Acceleration%20%5Bgeneric%5D |date=20090519183743 }} state that the unit name is “galileo”. The NIST and the BIPM are here considered as more authoritative sources regarding the proper unit name.</ref>

1伽等于1厘米每二次方秒（1 cm/s²）。

伽不是[[国际单位制|国际单位制]]的单位，但是在1978年，[[国际度量衡委员会|国际度量衡委员会]]决定伽可以与国际单位制单位并行使用，“直到国际度量衡委员会认为不再必要为止”。<ref name="SIbrochure"/><ref>''NIST Guide to SI Units''; Section 5, ''Units Outside the SI''; Subsection 5.2: ''[http://physics.nist.gov/Pubs/SP811/sec05.html#5.2 Units temporarily accepted for use with the SI] {{WebCite|url=https://www.webcitation.org/5YWY1pd2K?url=http://physics.nist.gov/Pubs/SP811/sec05.html#5.2 |date=20080612152327 |dateformat=iso }}''.</ref>

伽的命名是为了纪念第一个重力测量學者，[[意大利|意大利]]科学家[[伽利略·伽利莱|伽利略·伽利莱]]（{{lang|it|Galileo Galilei}}）。

